15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 4 O.S. 2021, Section 801, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 801. A. For purposes of this section:
19 1. The terms "place of public accommodation", "public
20 accommodation" and "service animal" shall have the same meaning as
21 such terms are defined in 28 C.F.R., Section 36.104. "Service
22 animal" does not include an emotional support animal or a therapy
23 animal;
24
